author: Source: Canada.com
title: US group urges government to relist Alibaba's Taobao on "notorious" fake mark... - Canada.com
text:
A clothing and shoe industry group is calling for the U.S. government to put Chinese e-commerce giant Alibaba's Taobao site back on its list of "Notorious Markets" for counterfeit goods. The American Apparel and Footwear Association said Tuesday that "counterfeits remain rampant" on Taobao three years after it was taken off the list.
 Canada.com.
